description: Stenhus Fastigheter i Norden AB engages in the investment, ownership and management of real estate. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 4 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2020-11-24. The Company’s business concept is to invest in properties and create the risk-adjusted return for the shareholders through a diversified property portfolio over time. Growth takes place through property acquisitions and property development.
name: Stenhus Fastigheter I Norden AB (publ)
